(87, 'Ummeed Housing Finance Pvt. Ltd', 4, 'Ummeed Housing Finance Private Limited (Ummeed) is a housing finance company registered with National Housing Bank (NHB) under the National Housing Bank Act, of 1987. Managed by a team of experienced professionals, we work with a common motive of providing home loans and loans against property to lower & middle-income Indian families.', '2016', 'https://www.ummeedhfc.com', '2023-04-10 07:00:00', 15),
(88, 'Virtusa', 4, 'Virtusa Corporation is a global provider of Digital Business Transformation, Digital Engineering, and Information Technology (IT) outsourcing services that accelerate our client’s journey to their Digital Future. Virtusa serves Global 2000 companies in Banking, Financial Services, Insurance, Healthcare, Telecommunications, Media, Entertainment, Travel, Manufacturing, and Technology industries.', '1993', 'https://www.virtusa.com', '2023-04-10 07:00:00', 15),
(89, 'Yudo Hot Runner India Pvt. Ltd', 2, 'YUDO is a company specializing in hot runner systems(\"HRS\") that produce environmentally friendly products with reduced resin waste. It has been applied in various industries to improve technology and quality, and to make products more beautiful, convenient, and safe.', '2000', 'https://www.yudo.com/en/', '2023-04-10 12:43:55', 15),
(90, 'Ummeed', 4, 'Ummeed Housing Finance Private Limited (Ummeed) is a housing finance company registered with National Housing Bank (NHB) under the National Housing Bank Act, of 1987. Managed by a team of experienced professionals, we work with a common motive of providing home loans and loans against property to lower & middle-income Indian families.', '2016', 'https://www.ummeedhfc.com', '2023-04-28 07:00:00', 2),
(91, 'RtCamp', 3, 'We deliver enterprise success for web publishing and digital commerce. The open-source technologies at the center of all our work help you unlock operational efficiency, develop new capabilities, remove vendor lock-in, reskill your teams, and reduce TCO. Our bespoke engineering solutions for Fortune 500 companies, government agencies, and household brands such as Google, Facebook, News UK, Penske Media Corp, and HCL, reach millions of people every day. We’re a fully distributed company with over 100 rtCampers and a WordPress VIP Gold agency partner.', '2009', 'https://rtcamp.com/', '2023-04-28 07:00:00', 19);
INSERT INTO `company` (`companyID`, `companyName`, `companyClass`, `companyDescription`, `companyEstablishment`, `companyWebsite`, `companyAddDate`, `companyAddedBy`) VALUES
(92, 'Quadeye', 3, 'Quadeye combines the best of both worlds: the opportunity and spirit of a startup and the stability of an established, experienced firm. Our employees work hard to solve interesting problems, and their results are rewarded. We value continuous learning—from our outcomes, from the environment, and from each other. By having the deepest possible understanding of the financial markets and translating that understanding into great automated trading strategies, we have built a distinct track record of success. We trade across many asset classes and instruments, using a variety of models, across the globe.', '2007', 'https://www.quadeye.com', '2023-04-28 07:00:00', 15),
(93, 'RDC Concrete', 2, 'RDC Concrete (India) Pvt Ltd is the largest independent ready-mixed concrete company in India.\r\nThe company manufactures and supplies Ready Mix Concrete (RMC). Its portfolio of customers includes construction companies, real estate developers, contractors, infrastructure companies, Road & Commercial Projects, and individual owners.', '1993', 'https://www.rdcconcrete.co', '2023-04-28 07:00:00', 14),
(94, 'RateGain', 3, 'RateGain Travel Technologies Limited is a global provider of SaaS solutions for travel and hospitality that works with 2800+ customers and 700+ partners in 100+ countries helping them accelerate revenue generation through acquisition, retention, and wallet share expansion. RateGain today is one of the world’s largest processors of electronic transactions, price points, and travel intent data helping revenue management, distribution and marketing teams across hotels, airlines, meta-search companies, package providers, car rentals, travel management companies, cruises, and ferries drive better outcomes for their business.', '2004', 'https://rategain.com/', '2023-04-29 09:31:00', 15),
(95, 'AMD', 2, 'AMD has driven innovation in high-performance computing, graphics, and visualization technologies. AMD employees are focused on building leadership,high-performance, and adaptive products that push the boundaries of what is possible. Billions of people, leading Fortune 500 businesses, and cutting-edge scientific research institutions around the world rely on AMD technology daily to improve how they live, work, and play.', '1969', 'https://www.amd.com', '2023-04-28 07:00:00', 13),
(96, 'Pentair', 3, 'Pentair is an American water treatment company incorporated in Ireland with tax residency in the UK, with its main U.S. office in Arden Hills, Minnesota. Pentair was founded in the US, with 65% of the company\'s revenue coming from the US and Canada as of 2017. Pentair was reorganized in 2014, shifting the corporate domicile from Switzerland to Ireland.', '1996', 'https://www.pentair.com/', '2023-04-28 07:00:00', 14),
(97, 'Gemini Solutions', 4, 'Gemini Solutions is an IT Consulting and Product Development firm. Our services provide clients with a flexibility to choose from an array of automation and application development solutions as well as giving them an option to choose from outsourcing, onshore or offshore engagement models. We cater to the diversified portfolio of clients across sectors such as banking & financial services, retail, healthcare, education and government sector', '2005', 'https://www.geminisolutions.com/', '2023-04-28 07:00:00', 20),
(98, 'Amantya Technology', 4, 'Amantya Technologies, Inc. is a USA-based product engineering and system integration company with operations in the USA, Canada, and India (Grogram, Bangalore & Nagpur). We are a global organization with proven expertise in next-generation technologies like 5G, IoT, AI ML, edge, and cloud services. Amantya\'s commitment to delivering excellence to our clients is fueled by our people. \'People First\' isn\'t just a mantra for us, but a way of life. Our team is a bunch of diverse individuals at different stages of their learning curve – experienced and quick learners, united by their commitment to keep upgrading their skills and bring their best each day. Amantya embodies a strong culture of innovation, collaboration, and a sense of ownership by embracing a growth mindset', '2018', 'https://amantyatech.com/', '2023-04-28 07:00:00', 19),
(99, 'JSW', 4, 'A $22 billion conglomerate, JSW Group is a part of the O.P. Jindal Group has strong footprints across various sectors namely, Steel, Energy, Minerals, Port & Infrastructure & Cement in multiple locations across India, the US, South America, and Africa.', '1982', 'https://www.jsw.in', '2023-04-28 07:00:00', 15),
(100, 'American Express', 3, 'The American Express Company (Amex) is an American multinational corporation specialized in payment card services headquartered at 200 Vesey Street in the Battery Park City neighborhood of Lower Manhattan in New York City. The company was founded in 1850 and is one of the 30 components of the Dow Jones Industrial Average. The company\'s logo, adopted in 1958, is a gladiator or centurion whose image appears on the company\'s well-known traveler\'s cheques, charge cards, and credit cards.', '1850', 'https://www.americanexpress.com/en-in/', '2023-04-28 07:00:00', 19),
(101, 'Chaayos', 3, 'Chaayos was born in November 2012 out of this premise - a contemporary interpretation of the chai adda, serving freshly made chai. Our focus is on serving your \"Meri Wali Chai\", a chai made exactly to our customers\' liking the minute they place their order - be it an adrak tulsi kadak chai or a paani kam elaichi cinnamon chai. Our option of 12 add-ons gives our customers a total of over 12,000 ways to make their chai at Chaayos.', '2012', 'https://chaayos.com/', '2023-04-29 08:46:03', 19),
(102, 'Contata Solutions', 4, 'Contata Solutions is an Information Technology and Services (ITES) company and has headquarters in Minneapolis, Minnesota, United States. Contata Solutions has 168 employees. It was founded in 2000. Contata Solutions specialises in website development and artificial intelligence. Contata Solutions is a private company.', '2000', 'https://www.contata.com/', '2023-04-28 07:00:00', 19),
(103, 'Galaxe Solution', 4, 'Galaxe is a leading global professional services company providing a broad range of services under iconic brands including Outsource to America® and GxFource®.Galaxe Solutions provides information technology services. The Company offers master data management, business intelligence, legacy application re-platforming, end-to-end project development, and enterprise IT services.', '1993', 'Companies Website Link:  https://www.galaxe.com', '2023-04-28 07:00:00', 19),
(104, 'KiwiTech', 4, 'KiwiTech has persistently led innovation toward creating a better tomorrow. Headquartered in New York, KiwiTech is a growing ecosystem of 500+ portfolio companies, 3000+ investors, and 300+ mentors committed to supporting innovators and sparking innovation globally. We help early to growth-stage startups build viable products, drive traction, raise capital, and scale their businesses.', '2009', 'https://www.kiwitech.com/', '2023-04-28 07:00:00', 15),
(105, 'PPL', 4, 'Phonographic Performance Limited also known as PPL India, is a performance rights organization, licensing its members’ sound recordings for communication to the public, in the areas of public performance and broadcast. PPL owns and/or controls the Public Performance rights of 350+ music labels, with more than 4.5 million international and domestic sound recordings. PPL India represents some of the world’s and India’s largest record labels, including Aditya Music, Lahari Music, Sony Music Entertainment, Speed Records, T-Series, Universal Music, and Warner Music, and is India’s largest and most respected public performance rights organization, in terms of both membership and revenue.', '1941', 'https://www.pplindia.org/', '2023-04-28 07:00:00', 15),
(106, 'PRESCIENT AND STRATEGIC INTELLIGENCE', 4, 'P&S Intelligence is a provider of market research and consulting services catering to the market information needs of burgeoning industries across the world. Providing the plinth of market intelligence, P&S as an enterprising research and consulting company believes in providing thorough landscape analyses on the ever-changing market scenario, to empower companies to make informed decisions and base their business strategies with astuteness.', '2014', 'https://www.psmarketresearch.com/', '2023-04-28 07:00:00', 15),
(107, 'IBM', 4, 'The International Business Machines Corporation (IBM) is an American multinational technology corporation headquartered in Armonk, New York, with operations in over 171 countries.  IBM produces and sells computer hardware, middleware and software and provides hosting and consulting services in areas ranging from mainframe computers to nanotechnology. IBM is also a major research organization, holding the record for most annual U.S. patents generated by a business (as of 2021) for 29 consecutive years.', '1911', 'https://www.ibm.com/in-en', '2023-04-29 08:40:11', 20),
(108, 'Cafe Coffee Day', 2, 'Cafe Coffee Day is India’s largest café chain and a favorite hangout where the young at heart unwind. Popularly known as CCD. We operate through Coffee Day Global Limited (CDGL), a subsidiary of Coffee Day Enterprises Limited. With Asia\'s second-largest network of coffee estates, Coffee Day has a rich and abundant source of coffee. The coffee goes all over the world to clients across the USA, Europe, and Japan, making us one of the top coffee exporters in the country.', '1996', 'https://www.cafecoffeeday.com/', '2023-04-28 07:00:00', 13),
(109, 'Crio.Do', 4, 'Crio.do is a platform that empowers developers to crack real-world industry problems and ‘learn by doing’.Crio’s mission is to empower developers with high-quality applied learning opportunities at scale and nurture the country’s product development talent to create great products.', '2019', 'https://www.crio.do', '2023-04-28 07:00:00', 13),
(110, 'DIGIT', 4, 'Digit is a general insurance company started by Kamesh Goyal and backed by the Fairfax Group. Its services include car insurance, travel insurance, home insurance, commercial vehicle insurance, and shop insurance. The company is driven by a mission to reimagine products and redesign pricing processes.', '2016', 'https://www.digit.com', '2023-04-28 07:00:00', 13),
(111, 'DIGIVERSAL CONSULTANT', 4, 'Digiversal is an Education-First technology company led by two change makers who propagate the nobility of literacy with a creativity mandate. We are a Scale-Stage tech startup based out of Noida, India, managing a large Study-Resource Digital Library for Undergraduate, Post-Graduate, and Ph.D. study levels with respect to research-based pedagogy.', '2015', 'https://www.digiversal.in', '2023-04-29 07:00:00', 13),
(112, 'Ernst & Young Global Delivery Services', 4, 'EY exists to build a better working world, helping create long-term value for clients, people, and society and building trust in the capital markets. Enabled by data and technology, diverse EY teams in over 150 countries provide trust through assurance and help clients grow, transform, and operate.', '1989', 'https://www.ey.com', '2023-04-29 07:00:00', 13),
(113, 'Adani', 4, 'Adani Group is a diversified organization that has created a world-class transport and utility infrastructure portfolio that has a pan-India presence. Adani Group has positioned itself as the market leader in its transport logistics and energy utility portfolio businesses focusing on large-scale infrastructure development in India with O & M practices benchmarked to global standards.\r\nAdani owes its success and leadership position to its core philosophy of ‘Nation Building’ driven by ‘Growth with Goodness’ - a guiding principle for sustainable growth.', '1988', 'https://www.adani.com/', '2023-04-29 07:00:00', 13),
(114, 'Tata Consultancy Services Codevita', 1, 'Tata Consultancy Services (TCS) is an Indian multinational information technology (IT) services and consulting company, headquartered in Mumbai, Maharashtra, India with its largest campus located in Chennai, Tamil Nadu, India. As of February 2021, TCS is the largest IT services company in the world by market capitalization ($200 billion). It is a subsidiary of the Tata Group and operates in 149 locations across 46 countries.\r\n\r\nIndustries\r\n●	Banking & Financial Services\r\n●	Capital Markets\r\n●	Consumer Goods & Distribution\r\n●	Communications, Media & Technology\r\n●	Education\r\n●	Energy, Resources & Utilities\r\n●	Hi-tech\r\n●	Insurance\r\n●	Life Sciences & Healthcare\r\n●	Manufacturing\r\n●	Public Services\r\n●	Retail\r\n●	Travel, Transportation & Hospitality', '1968', 'https://www.tcs.com/', '2023-04-29 07:00:00', 14),
(115, 'Tata Consultancy Services_nqt', 1, 'TCS is the second largest Indian Company by market capitalisation and is among the most valuable IT service brands worldwide. It is an Indian multinational information technology services and consulting company headquartered in Mumbai, Maharashtra and its largest campus located in Chennai, Tamil Nadu. In July 2022, it was reported that TCS had crossed 6 lakh or 600,000 employees worldwide.\r\nIndustries\r\n●	Banking & Financial Services\r\n●	Capital Markets\r\n●	Consumer Goods & Distribution\r\n●	Communications, Media & Technology\r\n●	Energy, Resources & Utilities\r\n●	Hi-tech\r\n●	Insurance\r\n●	Life Sciences & Healthcare\r\n●	Manufacturing\r\n●	Public Services\r\n●	Retail\r\n●	Travel, Transportation & Hospitality\r\n●	Education', '1968', 'Tata Consultancy Services', '2023-04-29 07:00:00', 14),
(116, ' Infosys ', 1, 'Infosys provides software development, maintenance, and independent validation services to companies in finance, insurance, manufacturing, and other domains. Infosys Limited is an Indian multinational information technology company that provides business consulting, information technology, and outsourcing services. The company was founded in Pune and is headquartered in Bangalore. One of its known products is Finacle which is a universal banking solution with various modules for retail and corporate banking. \r\n\r\nIndustries\r\n●	Aerospace & Defence\r\n●	Agriculture\r\n●	Automotive\r\n●	Communication Services\r\n●	Consumer Packaged Goods\r\n●	Education\r\n●	Engineering Procurement & Construction\r\n●	Financial Services\r\n●	Healthcare\r\n●	High Technology\r\n●	Industrial Manufacturing\r\n●	Information Services & Publishing\r\n●	Insurance\r\n●	Life Sciences\r\n●	Logistics & Distribution\r\n●	Media and Entertainment\r\n●	Mining\r\n●	Oil and Gas\r\n●	Private Equity\r\n●	Professional Services\r\n●	Public Sector\r\n●	Retail\r\n●	Travel and Hospitality\r\n●	Utilities\r\n●	Waste Management', '1981', 'www.infosys.com', '2023-04-29 07:00:00', 14),
(117, 'IndianOil Adani Gas', 2, 'IndianOil-Adani Gas Private Limited (IOAGPL), a 50:50 Joint venture of Indian Oil Corporation Limited (IOCL) and Adani Total Gas Limited (ATGL) incorporated in 2013 for providing Piped Natural Gas (PNG) in Industrial, Commercial, and Residential sectors and Compressed Natural Gas (CNG) in the transport sector. IOAGPL is one of those companies which enjoys strong parentage and is known for faster turnaround and best practices not only in India but also across the World. Our investments are creating a sustainable future.', '2013', 'https://ioagpl.com/', '2023-04-30 07:00:00', 14);

