(76, 49, 5, '7.2 - 8 LPA', '60% throughout (B.Tech CSE, CS, CSI, IT, ECE)', 'Technical Trainee', 'Online Test', 'This round contains 2 sections –\r\nSECTION 1- This section contains MCQ based on verbal ability, logical reasoning, numerical reasoning, and soft skills.\r\n---------------------------------------------------------------------\r\nSECTION 2- This section contains coding questions.', '60', 'Group Discussion', 'Group Discussion', '40 mins-60mins', 'Technical Round', '1. Write a program to find the second largest element in an Array.\r\n2. Write a program for Bubble Sort code.\r\n3. Write SQL Queries related to Joint and Group By.\r\n4. What are the Constraints in SQL?\r\n5. What are the similarities and differences between PRIMARY and UNIQUE Key?\r\n6. What are the command types in SQL?\r\n7. What is DOM in Java-Script?\r\n8. Write a program for Insertion Sort.\r\n9. Tell me something about the project.\r\n10. Write a Query for Max Element.\r\n11. Write a Query for ‘Letter Starting with A’.\r\n12. Write a Query to insert your name and number in the Table.\r\n13. What is the difference between Abstraction and Interface?\r\n14. What is the difference between String Buffer and String Builder?\r\n15. Define String Reversal.\r\n16. What is the difference between DELETE and TRUNCATE?\r\n17. Write a difference between function Overriding and function Overloading.\r\n18. What is Exception Handling in Java?\r\n19. What is the difference between Hash-map and Hash-Tree?\r\n20. What is the difference between STATIC Keyword and FINAL Keyword?\r\n21. Explain Public Static Void Main (String args []).\r\n22. Write a code for finding Prime Numbers in a given series.\r\n23. Write Vector Sort of pairs by Second Element.\r\n', '40 mins-60 mins', 'HR', '1. Tell me something about yourself.\r\n2. Tell me something about your native place.\r\n3. Why do you want to join Gemini Solutions?\r\n4. Tell me something about your family background.\r\n5. Explain the technologies used in y