(79, 78, 2, '5.5 LPA', 'NA', 'ASSOCIATE MARKETING PROFILE', 'Group Discussion', 'Topics :\r\n\r\n1. What are the advantages and disadvantages of working from home versus working from the office?\r\n2. In what ways has the COVID-19 pandemic affected the mental health of individuals, and what can be done to address these impacts?\r\n', '40 - 60 min', 'Profile Interview + HR', 'Technical Questions\r\n \r\n1. Tell me about yourself.\r\n2. Tell me something about your Internship.\r\n3. What are the important steps in Marketing?\r\n4. Why is Marketing important nowadays?\r\n5. What is the role of an Associate Marketing profile?\r\n6. What are some valuable lessons and experiences gained from internships in marketing, and how can they be applied in future marketing roles?\r\n7. Why did you choose B.Tech, if you want to go in Marketing field?\r\n8. Why did you want to join Innovaccer only?\r\n9. Various guesstimates were given, such as guessing the dimensions of the hall and the office, their capacities, etc.\r\n10. You are from an engineering background, why do you want to join marketing or sales?\r\n11. Which phone do you use? How many users in India are currently using that phone?\r\n12. Did a telephone conversation on how I will do sales? (Case study)\r\n13. They gave me software and asked how I would sell that software to companies.\r\n\r\n\r\nHR Questions\r\n \r\n\r\n1. Where do you see yourself in the next 5 years?\r\n2. Explain Testing and Split Testing.\r\n3. What is the Email Matrix?\r\n4. What is the use of Google Analytics?\r\n5. Any internship experience regarding Marketing profiles?\r\n6. Why B.Tech if you wanted to go into marketing?\r\n7. Why did you want to join Innovaccer only?\r\n8. What is the difference between Sales and Marketing?\r\n9. How many Rotis are made in India every day?\r\n10. What are the terms used in Email marketing /Digital Marketing?\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', '40 - 60 min', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', 'Approved', 'https://prepinsta.com/\r